headline: U.S. Bank Freight Payment Index: Truck freight market continues to contract
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, February 04, 2025--The truck freight market closed out 2024 with further declines in shipments and spending, according to the latest U.S. Bank Freight Payment Index. Fourth quarter shipment volume was down 4.7% compared to the prior quarter while spending dropped 2.2%.
